import { Input ,Form,FormGroup,Label,Button,FormText, Card } from "reactstrap";
import './FormComponent.css';

export function FormComponent(params) {

    return(
        
    <Form >
  <FormGroup>
    <Label for="exampleEmail">
      Nom
    </Label>

      id="exampleEmail"
      name="email"
      placeholder="with a placeholder"

    />
  </FormGroup>
  <FormGroup>
    <Label for="exampleEmail">
      Prenom
    </Label>
    <Input 
      id="exampleEmail"
      name="email"
      placeholder="with a placeholder"
      type="email"
    />
  </FormGroup>
  <FormGroup>

      Email
    </Label>
    <Input 
      id="exampleEmail"
      name="email"
      placeholder="with a placeholder"
      type="email"
    />
  </FormGroup>
  
  <FormGroup>

      Mot de passe
    </Label>

      type="password"
    />

  <Button>

  </Button>








  
</Form>

}
